Disable GitHub Copilot features and AI telemetry

Removes the built-in Copilot extension from the build pipeline entirely:
- Removes compileCopilotExtensionBuildTask and ripgrep shim from gulpfile.reh.ts
- Removes extensions/copilot from build/npm/dirs.ts (no npm install)
- Removes copilot-related npm scripts (watch-copilot, copilot:setup, etc.)

Also: inlines IExperimentationFilterProvider to remove tas-client dependency,
disables Copilot extension version tracking, forces chat entitlement to hidden,
defaults AI edit telemetry stats to false, and marks mermaid-chat-features as
not included.

